GeneralComments: Chargy is a public charging network offering wholesale services to charging service providers who sell the service to final users. Each charging service provider can have its own pricing. On the chargy.lu website, you can find a list of charging service providers. By now (March 2019) there are about 300 Chargy stations in Luxembourg, by end 2020 there should be 800.
